### UPDATE
### Modificar un usuario
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/{{idToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "CARLOS",
    "lastName": "LÓPEZ"
}

### UPDATE PASSWORD
### Modificar contraseña de un usuario
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/{{idToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "password": "newpassword123"
}

### INCREMENT SELLS
### Incrementar ventas de un usuario
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/{{idToUpdate}}/increment-sells

### DELETE
### Borrar un usuario
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/{{idToDelete}}

